{"tid":1577641,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"希望大家對於美國法案就算通過左，都唔好太興奮","createTime":"2019-09-17T20:25:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T22:05:57.000Z","uid":287214,"like":62,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"fe5af9032d36006abffca8f29ef44868efe32b44","tid":1577641,"uid":287214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T20:25:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我知道唔啱聽，但係都想講兩句。<br />\n<br />\n利申：住美國<br />\n<br />\n而家香港人權民主法案如箭在弦，我了解大家都好興奮有呢一個外援。但係我想講，人哋通過左個法案即係等於枱面多咗一把刀，但係把刀用唔用，同埋點用係好因應人哋嘅國家需要而定。通過左當然係好事，我亦絕對希望有阻嚇性。<br />\n<br />\n遠水總好過冇水，但係近火都係自己要救。<br />\n<br />\n多謝完美國放多把刀響枱面，大家就要收拾心情用自己嘅能力繼續行落去，唔好存在太大幻想，因為我唔想大家失望。<br />\n<br />\n民主自由唔係中國會俾你，亦都唔係美國會俾你，而係要我地自己出盡所有能力先至可能有一線機會。<br />\n<br />\n大家共勉<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n　</span>"},{"pid":"996e07bc2946eacea4182750b07df85e054ca444","tid":1577641,"uid":108571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T20:39:52.000Z","msg":"認同<br />\n能夠制裁未必等於我地贏<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc4aae642c6f262cfdd7ae04dba7a5bf62a18678","tid":1577641,"uid":167548,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T20:41:24.000Z","msg":"我覺得關鍵是9.29 anti chinazi global protests <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80972b52e4d539e819e81253b4ac7c38db96d4d9","tid":1577641,"uid":7270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T20:41:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ba39f7abf7bc022672b6d3c423b9964220a73056","tid":1577641,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T20:42:00.000Z","msg":"但是沒咩宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可唔可以嚟個全球登報啊！"},{"pid":"dbe4908edc5ae8de564d24c2db86e900d32ecf84","tid":1577641,"uid":86277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc4aae642c6f262cfdd7ae04dba7a5bf62a18678","tid":1577641,"uid":167548,"like